00:13:48.000 --> 00:13:56.000
No one wanted to do it because if you make a mistake, the whole thing would crash if you miss out a comma or anything like that.

00:13:56.000 --> 00:14:00.000
So the first two refused, so I was next in line, I was the third in line.

00:14:00.000 --> 00:14:03.000
So they asked if I wanted to do it, I said yes.

00:14:03.000 --> 00:14:07.000
So when I went in there, I remember, you know, the speed was very fast.

00:14:07.000 --> 00:14:09.000
My feet was 19,000.

00:14:09.000 --> 00:14:11.000
We all very fast, you know.

00:14:11.000 --> 00:14:17.000
