00:14:57.000 --> 00:15:03.000
Likely means either you're good, likely, or you're no good.

00:15:03.000 --> 00:15:06.000
You know, they always gave me the middle.

00:15:06.000 --> 00:15:13.000
But anyway, I wanted to go in for, I wanted to graduate higher, the next level.

00:15:13.000 --> 00:15:16.000
And to the next level, I put in for it.

