And if it's worn down, you know.

00:15:51.000 --> 00:15:53.000
So he gave me those tips.

00:15:53.000 --> 00:15:54.000
It was good.

00:15:54.000 --> 00:16:03.000
But anyway, and he said, when the question be on drugs.

00:16:03.000 --> 00:16:08.000
