So then, you know what happened next, the union men on my side.

00:17:04.000 --> 00:17:07.000
And I knew some of the union men, they were so good, you know, helped me.

00:17:07.000 --> 00:17:10.000
And they sort of took it up with them.

00:17:10.000 --> 00:17:16.000
But, you know, later on, one thing you know, in hindsight, you know, you could have done push it further, but I didn't.

00:17:16.000 --> 00:17:17.000
You know.

