And then he said, had we given it to you, there was a question why we gave it to you who had likely to be fitted.

00:17:24.000 --> 00:17:28.000
And those, there was someone done just as well as you who had fitted.

00:17:28.000 --> 00:17:32.000
So they caused a lot of problems, you know.

